# AI-Powered Task Management System

## Project Overview

The AI-Powered Task Management System is a machine learning-based solution designed to analyze software project tasks and predict their priority using historical task data. The project applies data preprocessing, Natural Language Processing (NLP), Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), and machine learning techniques to improve task prioritization.

This project demonstrates an end-to-end data science workflow, from raw data processing to model training and evaluation.

---

# Objectives

- Perform data preprocessing and cleaning.
- Analyze task management datasets using EDA.
- Apply NLP techniques on task descriptions.
- Predict task priority using Machine Learning.
- Optimize model performance using GridSearchCV.
- Compare Random Forest and XGBoost models.

